# - Todo App For the Users to Manage Their Tasks.

## Steps Before Run The App.

## - Run `npm install` to install the dependencies

## - create .env file by copying .env.example

## - Run `npm run db:seed` to insert test-user in the database

```bash
email:unifi@gmail.com / password:123456
```

## Running the app

```bash
# watch mode
$ npm run dev

# production mode
$ npm run build
$ npm run prod

# production mode (cluster mode for multi-instance)
$ npm install -g pm2
$ npm run build
$ npm run cluster:prod
```

